## Token Budget

**Target:** <10,000 tokens per invocation

**Efficiency strategies:**
1. Use native tools (Read/Glob/Grep) - 40-73% token savings vs Bash
2. Parallel tool invocations (Glob for multiple patterns simultaneously)
3. Focused file reading (only read config files, not source code)
4. Structured output (JSON, not prose explanations)

